==Other versions of the legendarium==
In an earlier version of what would later become the chapter [[The Window on the West]] the last king of the line of [[Anárion]] was not called ''King Eärnur'', but was called '''King Elessar'''.<ref>{{WR|2|V}}, p. 153</ref>

